title: Burn $LOBS in treasury? Proposal #1
body:
Out of 6,751 total $LOBS NFTs, 3464 have been matched to addresses and in the process of being claimed. There are 3,287 left in the DAO's treasury, or 49% of total supply.
https://twitter.com/10b57e6da0/status/1446786577859072001

Shall the DAO burn $LOBS in treasury?

Pros:
• $LOBS will be rare
• The DAO has existing cashflow thanks to 5.25% royalties (70% of 7.5%) on purchase
• LobsterDAO chat will get more polluted by DAO drama

Cons:
• The DAO will miss on cool things that could be done with undistributed $LOBS
• Some Klibansky art will be destroyed, potentially including rare pieces
• More intense and meaningful governance activity within the DAO
author: 0x2992aE1837fd3E5722495d078b599E0b9C5B2Cb5
